  "translations": {
    "en": "Abu Abdillah (peace be upon him) said: The Prophets and the Messengers are upon four categories. There is a Prophet who is informed within himself, without going beyond others; and there is a Prophet who sees in sleep and hears the voice, and does not see him (the angel) while awake, and was not sent to anyone, and upon him is an Imam — similar to how Ibrahim was above Lot (peace be upon him).",
